Below you will find all the server sizing specifications tables for Windows operating systems.


  <summary>Small Segment - Customer sizing up to <b>5</b> users</summary>
  <p>
    Within the 5 users, the customer is considered small, so we can hypothesize a single server solution that will contain both the ARM / Fluentis web servers and the SQL database.
  </p>
  <div>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th></th>
        <th>Minimum</th>
        <th>Recommended</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Operating System</td> 
        <td>Windows Server 2019</td>
        <td>Windows Server 2022</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>CPU</td> 
        <td>Intel Xeon 2.5GHz</td>
        <td>Intel Xeon 3.0GHz</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>RAM</td> 
        <td>32GB</td>
        <td>32GB</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Storage</td> 
        <td>SSD (min. 10GB for ARM and Fluentis)</td>
        <td>4 x SSD (raid 5)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Database</td> 
        <td>Microsoft SQL Server 2019</td>
        <td>Microsoft SQL Server 2022</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>


